# --- byreis runtime artifacts (never commit secrets/keys) ---
# Key material is matched by EXTENSION (covers any path/depth) — these are the
# real exposure surface; byreis loads the admin key from keychain/env/key-file,
# never from a tracked in-repo identity dir.
*.key
*.key.pub
*.age
.byreis.local.yaml
# Belt-and-braces: an accidental repo-ROOT runtime identity dir a dev/user
# might create locally. ROOT-ANCHORED (leading slash) so it CANNOT match the
# source package internal/core/crypto/identity/ (or any nested identity/ dir).
/identity/
# Throwaway crypto-spike PROOF CODE only. Durable gate artifacts
# (FINDINGS.md, REQUIREMENTS.md) live in design/ and ARE committed.
# design/ (DESIGN.md, ADRs, reqs) and docs/ (public docs) are tracked.
spike/

